videoSnippet.title: Vassily, Your King is on d4!
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Vassily Ivanchuk vs Wei Yi
Ivanchuk - Wei Yi (2017), Hoogeveen NED, rd 3, Oct-23 
Queen's Gambit Declined: Ragozin Defense (D38) 

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Nf3 d5 5. cd5 ed5 6. Bg5 h6 7. Bh4 O-O 8. e3 Bf5 9. Rc1 Nbd7 10. Qb3 Bc3 11. Rc3 c6 12. Nd2 Qa5 13. f3 Rfe8 14. Kf2 Rac8 15. Be2 c5 16. dc5 Rc5 17. Rhc1 g5 18. Bg3 Re3 19. Ke3 d4 20. Kd4 Re5 21. Bd3 Be6 22. Qb7 Kg7 23. Ne4 Nd5 24. Be5 Ne5 25. Rc5

A six-game match between experienced Ukrainian super-GM Vassily Ivanchuk and upcoming Chinese talent Wei Yi is played in Hoogeveen, the Netherlands, between October 21 and October 26, 2017. Part of the 21st Hoogeveen Schaaktoernooi, the match is held concurrently with Van Foreest - Adhiban (2017) and three open Swiss System tournaments.
